# =========================
# Machine Learning — large / unused model files
# (App only needs douala_xgb_model_ii.pkl & maroua_xgb_model_ii.pkl)
# =========================
# Random Forest models (~190 MB each — exceeds GitHub 100 MB limit)
Model/douala_rf_model_ii.pkl
Model/maroua_rf_model_ii.pkl
Model/*_rf_model_*.pkl

# LSTM models (not used by deployed app)
Model/douala_lstm_model_ii.pkl
Model/maroua_lstm_model_ii.pkl
Model/*_lstm_model_*.pkl

# Optional: older/best checkpoints (uncomment if you don't want these in Git)
# Model/best_douala_xgb.pkl
# Model/best_maroua_xgb.pkl
# Model/best_*.pkl

